HEADWORD: Tripetaloid
<hw>Tri*pet"al*oid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>tri-</ets> + <ets>petaloid</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Having the form or appearance of three petals; appearing as if
furnished with three petals.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tripetalous</ent>⟦br⟧
